thread.title: UNT lists co-backup quarterbacks
thread.title_full: UNT lists co-backup quarterbacks | Dallas Morning News

author: Brett Vito
title: UNT lists co-backup quarterbacks
text:
DENTON -- UNT made one small adjustment to its quarterback depth chart Monday after a loss to Iowa dropped the Mean Green to 0-3. Andrew McNulty remains UNT's starter heading into practice this week and will be backed up by DaMarcus Smith and Josh Greer, who are listed together at second on the depth chart.
Greer went 2 for 6 for 30 yards but threw an interception that linebacker Bo Bower returned 88 yards for a touchdown.
